<div style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">
<span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #595959;">Hi {{lead.First Name:default=there}},&nbsp;</span>
</div> 
<div style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">
<span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #595959;"></span>
<br>
</div> 
<div style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">
<span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #595959;">Through <a href="https://pivotal.io/customers" target="_blank" style="font-weight: 400; color: #00ae9e; text-decoration: none;">our work with some of the world’s leading organizations</a> we’ve learned what works and what doesn’t on the journey to Application Transformation. From experience, here are our top 4 tips:&nbsp;</span>
</div> 
<div style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">
<span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #595959;"></span>
<br>
</div> 
<div style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">
<span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #595959;">Start small - START WITH ONE BUSINESS UNIT AND A HANDFUL OF APPS<br>We recommend starting with a set of 5-10 applications built over the last five years using that are of low technical risk and of high business relevance.&nbsp;</span>
</div> 
<div style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">
<span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #595959;"></span>
<br>
</div> 
<div style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">
<span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #595959;">Learn by Doing - BUILD A COOKBOOK OF PATTERNS INFORMED BY MOVING INITIAL APPS INTO PROD<br>Form an internal consulting function around app transformation and augment internal staff (who own and lead the initiative) with external resources (that can scale and offer an economic advantage) in a way that ramps over time. The objective is to get 5-10 applications moved into production while capturing lessons/techniques as recipes to streamline and accelerate future efforts.&nbsp;</span>
</div> 
<div style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">
<span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #595959;"></span>
<br>
</div> 
<div style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">
<span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #595959;">Break Big Things Into Small Things - BREAK “SLICES” OF COMPLEX SYSTEMS INTO PIVOTAL CLOUD FOUNDRY (PCF)<br>Monoliths often span multiple subsystems and data sources and dozens of deployables across a network of servers and mainframe backends. By breaking down complex systems into lightweight microservices, you can scale horizontally on a cloud. <br><br>Automate Everything - REDUCE MANUAL PROCESS ACROSS THE PATH-TO-PRODUCTION<br>We recommend drawing a ​value stream map​ of the end-to-end path to production (for the initial apps only) to identify opportunities to reduce waste through automation.<br></span>
</div> 
<div style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">
<span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #595959;"></span>
<br>
</div> 
<div style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">
<span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #595959;">If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to us <a href="https://pivotal.io/contact" target="_blank" style="font-weight: 400; color: #00ae9e; text-decoration: none;">here</a> or visit our <a href="https://content.pivotal.io/application-modernization" target="_blank" style="font-weight: 400; color: #00ae9e; text-decoration: none;">Application Modernization resource center</a>.</span>
</div> 
<div style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">
<span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #595959;"></span>
<br>
</div> 
<div style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">
